<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Appointment Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #007BFF;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .appointment-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .appointment-details p {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 5px 0;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #218838;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Appointment Notification</h2>
    <p>Dear Dr. <%=doctorName%>,</p>
    <p>We are pleased to inform you that a new appointment has been scheduled. Below are the details:</p>

    <div class="appointment-details">
      <p><strong>Patient Name:</strong> <%=patientName%></p>
      <p><strong>Appointment Date:</strong>  <%=date%></p>
      <p><strong>Appointment Time:</strong>  <%=time%></p>
      <p><strong>Reason for Visit:</strong>  <%=reason%></p>
    </div>

    <p>If you need to reschedule or require further information, please feel free to contact us.</p>
    
    <a class="btn">Contact Us</a>
    <p>Thank you for your attention.</p>
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>xyz clinic</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
